title: American horror story murder house - young Tate meets Mrs Montgomery
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Tate seemed like such a sweet kid. When he told Nora, "I wish you were my mommy", my heart shattered into a million pieces.
she would have been a good mother... at times.
"Dry your tears. Life is too short for so much sorrow." Despite its hit or misses with plot, AHS does have some great quotes.
I love Lily Rabe, she's so beautiful and sweet
as if any kid in the world would go into the basement... even if they had lights xD
